                    <p>I'm a seasoned product guy who loves helping startups capture new ground.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <!-- MARS LANDING ANIMATION -->
                <%= render partial: "layouts/mars_landing" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="overview" class="section--white">
    <div class="container text-xs-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
                <p><kbd>puts 'hello world'</kbd></p>
                <p>Here you'll find a collection of my startup adventures, some examples of my development and design experimentation and handful hobby projects.</p>
