</section>

<section id="stories" class="section--grey text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h5 class="section--title mb-2">Stories</h5>
                <p>Slowly growing a collection of my startup stores, rants, etc.</p>
            </div>
            <%= render partial: "projects/project_card" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="section--white text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5 class="section--title">Who's This Gordon Guy?</h5>
                <p>The answer to that question is probably best answered with what I'm working on at the time the quesiton is asked. Currently, I'm situated with an exciting, young startup we've dubbed <a href="https://wirkn.com" target="_blank">Wirkn</a>. There I head up the product and engineering team as the company's CPO.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5 class="section--title">Getting Here...</h5>
                <p>Ten years ago, I stepped foot on <a href="https://uwaterloo.ca" target="_blank">UWaterloo</a> campus for the first time. With a graphing calculator in one hand and a Big Gulp in the other. I couldn't have been more excited about my future in Mechanical Engineering.<p>
                <p>Little did I know that just one year later I'd be trading my iron ring in for late nights with my trusty MacBook on a beat-up couch, in a colorfully decorated startup office.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5 class="section--title">And Now...?</h5>
                <p>Since then I've helped grow, sell and gracefully bring to a close and a number of startup companies across North Ameria.</p>
                <p>I invite you to enjoy reading some of my stories and to checkout my hobby projects.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="sites" class="section--grey text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 mb-3">
                <h5 class="section--title">Hobby Projects</h5>
                <p>
                    Some of the small projects I've been working on to keep my skills sharp.<br>
                    <small class="text-muted">Please note, I've used the free tier of Heroku to host many of these sites. They can take up to 30s to load.</small>
                </p>
                <div class="card-columns">
                    <%= render partial: "sites/site_card" %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <a href="https://github.com/gjrevans" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-github mr-1"></i>GitHub</a>
                <a href="https://codepen.io/gjrevans/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-codepen mr-1"></i>CodePen</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="technologies" class="section--white text-xs-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-xs-center">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2 mb-3">
                <h5 class="section--title">Technologies</h5>
                <p>With the risk of sounding like a <del>crotchety old man</del> brilliant engineer, I tend to advocate for the use of <a href="http://mcfunley.com/choose-boring-technology" target="_blank">'boring technologies'</a>. Tools that get the job done and don't introduce unnecessary complexities when time is of the essence.</p>
                <p>Some of the technologies I love to work with.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <%= render partial: "layouts/technologies" %>
        </div>
